ac{1}{-x}$ 的平移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":523}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"8afkgc","at":1769671148815}},"smart_blocks:01-数学教学/试卷/功底考/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.02759123,0.00305119,0.03426683,-0.05234737,0.01627053,0.00077706,0.00013163,-0.02128393,0.0243864,-0.00147756,0.02254813,-0.04146334,0.02860122,-0.00329839,0.02179392,0.02319992,-0.01960566,-0.03303822,-0.05330291,-0.00600262,0.14347103,-0.04126156,-0.01532583,-0.0797358,0.04414661,0.04447077,0.04467876,-0.0640521,0.01719722,-0.19251308,-0.00068676,0.02380216,0.00708437,0.02536235,0.03907997,-0.03497533,-0.00567814,0.06796251,-0.06960175,0.03063614,-0.00665056,0.07370237,0.04018158,-0.00982725,0.04304785,-0.02941131,-0.01301124,-0.0460006,0.02172921,-0.03356467,-0.06059992,-0.0081754,-0.01604628,0.0263057,0.02634766,0.00640181,0.00511376,0.05405396,-0.01163474,-0.00929295,0.04687833,0.00875373,-0.22863978,0.01009061,0.04858762,-0.01574498,0.00100749,-0.03957952,0.05887378,0.09229045,-0.02939552,0.01030824,0.02258393,0.04805714,0.01433329,0.00645153,0.02267809,-0.0124678,-0.05525706,-0.05112628,-0.01569881,0.07811486,0.03695928,-0.01199171,-0.00460138,0.00659762,-0.00237487,-0.10753667,-0.01318902,-0.04424951,0.00841832,-0.02179947,0.01544746,0.04193899,-0.03937024,0.028201,0.0133318,0.02606221,-0.01279673,0.09811902,-0.04930369,0.07975223,0.00343504,-0.07230745,0.00694342,-0.04304131,-0.03134783,-0.09476389,-0.00528152,-0.01146678,-0.02238064,-0.02062645,0.07194255,-0.0814976,-0.00383461,0.00058948,0.07500973,0.03736022,-0.01603521,0.00943907,0.03225189,0.05778332,0.03486459,-0.03633485,-0.00169392,-0.07545909,0.0131689,0.00844724,0.05150687,0.05362037,0.02877604,0.00441014,0.02426639,-0.007273